{{flavour|A ring that allows its wearer to see those things hidden from view by magic.}}

A '''ring of see invisible''' allows its wearer to see creatures that are invisible (either intrinsically or through use of the [[Invisibility]] spell).

==Desirability==
A ring of see invisible is invaluable when trying to kill invisible monsters such as [[unseen horror]]s, [[ghost moth]]s, and some of the demons of [[Hell]]. However, as its worthelss against visible monsters, it is not worth a dedicated ring slot. Swap this in as needed.

